text:
EFL   set to spend a season at Wembley in 2018 after RFU reject Twickenhan move as Stamford Bridge is renovated 
The Blues will need a temporary home for three years after planning permission granted for new 60,000 but Twickenham residents reject league leaders using home of rugby by Warren Haughton
